### Create Document whit Items

POST {{Api_URL}}/api/Document
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "numeroDocumento": "PRE-001",
  "tipoDocumento": 1,
  "fecha": null,
  "estado": 1,
  "iva": null,
  "idCliente": "{{id_cliente}}",
